name: AUDX
description: AUDX is a token issued by a licensed Australian exchange, focusing on RWA (Real-World Assets) projects, dedicated to digitizing real-world assets via blockchain technology. As a compliant and transparent platform, AUDX offers secure and efficient digital asset services, enabling users to seamlessly access global financial markets. Our goal is to drive deep integration between RWA and the crypto world, empowering investors and businesses worldwide.
